OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOutbreaks of
OL,6,Frain, heavy in places, will clear away
OL,7,Feast through the evening. Then it will
OL,8,Fstay dry overnight with clear spells
OL,9,Fbut some low cloud will spread into
OL,10,FDumfries and Galloway.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FIt will be largely cloudy
OL,13,Fthrough the day with some showery
OL,14,Foutbreaks of rain which may turn heavy
OL,15,Fat times.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,18,Fon Sunday with a chance of showers.
OL,19,FSunny spells and a few showers on
OL,20,FMonday and Tuesday. Remaining cooler
OL,21,Fthan recent days.
